description:
Danny recaps part 1 of The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion, which featured a Kathy-themed set, hand makeup, and a Halloween crossover. Then Danny dives into Vanderpump Rules, where 2 people got engaged, Brock's story comes to the forefront, and Tom criticizes his wife's haircut.


Vanderpump Rules Recap: 27:40ish
